{"tid":1220631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭文貴又中 香港美國領事館換領事","createTime":"2019-06-14T04:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T10:09:40.000Z","uid":54373,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"932b875197dccf14cc62e40397cdd8c7fcb318f9","tid":1220631,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:51:49.000Z","msg":"美國駐香港及澳門總領事館宣佈，國務卿蓬佩奧已委任史墨客先生，接替唐偉康先生，為下一任美國駐香港及澳門總領事，並將於二零一九年七月起履新。<a href=\"http://ow.ly/RkhB50uDLph\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fow.ly%2FRkhB50uDLph&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=0039b365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ow.ly/RkhB50uDLph</a><br />\n<br />\nThe U.S. Consulate General Hong Kong and Macau is pleased to announce that Secretary Pompeo has selected Hanscom Smith to be the new Consul General representing the United States to Hong Kong and Macau, succeeding Consul General Kurt W. Tong beginning in July 2019.  <a href=\"https://hk.usconsulate.gov/pr-2019061401/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.usconsulate.gov%2Fpr-2019061401%2F&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=ce0de0bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.usconsulate.gov/pr-2019061401/</a>"},{"pid":"103aaeede65ec13f065a2712fee5768a0ee85168","tid":1220631,"uid":54373,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:52:35.000Z","msg":"5毛: 無范冰冰片 就算你講中一百樣都唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb1593e3c2113657a1f0eb21c6e4c32b3c3b6fe","tid":1220631,"uid":21277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ffbf6962a0552387228f24344402c2aa46d1cd9","tid":1220631,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:58:48.000Z","msg":"新任咩底子"},{"pid":"3f03276aa2d02a670447