tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:10:23.000Z","msg":"現任總領事唐偉康7月任滿離港並加入私人機構工作。<br />\n<br />\n身爲高級職業外交官的史墨客先生，出生於緬因州，配偶為吕英宗（Eric Lu）。他懂中文、法文、丹麥語及柬埔寨語。 史墨客獲委任前在國務院出任主管中國事務處的副助理國務卿。<br />\n<br />\n他曾出任美國駐上海總領事，國務院中國及蒙古事務處處長，也曾經在多個美國駐外使領館工作，包括喀麥隆、丹麥、柬埔寨、泰國、阿富汗及中國。另外，他還在國務院的日本事務處及美國在台協會任職，亦曾領導過美國在伊拉克穆薩納省的重建工作。<br />\n<br />\n史墨客畢業於喬治城大學（Georgetown University），擁有倫敦政治經濟學院（London School of Economics and Political Science）及普林斯頓大學（Princeton University）碩士學位，巴黎政治學院（Sciences Po Paris）政治研究證書。他曾以美國外交關係協會國際關係學人身份在日本交流研究。"},{"pid":"9030b7a71ad45ade409b2bd6b2a58dc8cb31b2ac","tid":1220631,"uid":21275,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:17:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f0878b6ecbad3345f172116775b03f870a1d337","tid":1220631,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:17:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1361af97740f5cccb1b7c88f9a33f3fe4d7a8ee9","tid":1220631,"uid":254371,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:20:06.000Z","msg":"美帝香港領事次次都係三年換一次，仲要係次次都係七月換<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Consulate_General_of_the_United_States,_Hong_Kong_and_Macau\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FConsulate_General_of_the_United_States%2C_Hong_Kong_and_Macau&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=9a4680e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Consulate_General_of_the_United_States,_Hong_Kong_and_Macau</a>"},{"pid":"9982a473fb9f2dae820140fc3057ed22cd01551a","tid":1220631,"uid":194415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:22:24.000Z","msg":"如果化武都中埋<br />\n我地就嬴<br />\n<br />\n化武 ＝ 聯合國必須介入<br />\n又調查隊、又出兵"},{"pid":"727ac8010c3e1aec20ee4f41be28f2bbbdb0555b","tid":1220631,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9982a473fb9f2dae820140fc3057ed22cd01551a","tid":1220631,"uid":194415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:22:24.000Z","msg"